    "amount": "30%",
    "program": "IRA Section 25D Residential Clean Energy Credit",
    "notes": "30% of total cost with no cap. Includes equipment, labor, permits. ACTIVE through 2032 (NOT affected by the 25C expiration that hit windows/HVAC/insulation on Dec 31 2025 — 25D is a different section of the IRA). Applies to solar PV, solar water heating, battery storage 3kWh+, geothermal, fuel cells. Step-down to 26% in 2033 and 22% in 2034 under current statute."
